Class ConfigServiceActor

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.services.cs.akka.ConfigServiceActor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging

    public class ConfigServiceActor
extends java.lang.Object
implements akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging
    An Akka actor class implementing the Config Service.

    param: configManager the configManager to use to access the repo param: registerWithLoc if true, register with the config service using configManager.name
